		        <p style="background: #81B214; color:black; border-radius:20px; padding:20px; font-weight: 500; font-size:17px;">Welcome to Veggie Village, where authentic Indian flavors meet a world-class dining experience. We take pride in bringing you the rich heritage of Indian cuisine, crafted with the finest ingredients and traditional cooking techniques. From the bold and aromatic spices of North India to the delicate and flavorful dishes of the South, our menu is a celebration of India's diverse culinary landscape.

